  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dab\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Another death in the fuel line",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that a person who was in a fuel queue at the IOC filling station on Payagala Galle Road under Beruwala Divisional Secretariat died today (7) after being admitted to the Kalutara Nagoda Hospital due to an emergency.",
        "Pyagala Police confirms that this person was admitted to the Kalutara Nagoda General Hospital at around 1 am this morning and died at the hospital around 5 am. Another person died in a fuel queue.",
        "Hospital sources say that the deceased person is a 60-year-old resident of Moratuwa area."
      ],
